# Cloudflare Pages redirects. fooseroo.app is served by Cloudflare Pages, which —
# unlike the GitHub Pages origin — does NOT serve our 404.html for unknown paths;
# it returned a typeless, empty 404, which browsers saved as a ".txt" download.
# Route the deeplink paths (opened only when the Android App Links did NOT catch
# them, i.e. no app installed / iOS / desktop) to the landing, carrying the
# original path in ?go= so the landing offers Play Store + Web and the web tile
# opens the matching in-app view. (Installed Android app intercepts these before
# Cloudflare is ever reached.)
/m/*  /?go=/m/:splat  302
/t/*  /?go=/t/:splat  302
/g/*  /?go=/g/:splat  302
